ah be pleased with him, and Ibn Mas\u2019ud visited his household but did not find him, so he sought permission to enter, greeted them with peace, and requested a drink. They dispatched a servant girl to bring him a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43851,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/07\/03\/ahmad-cursing-makruh\/","url_meta":{"origin":32169,"position":1},"title":"Ahmad on Curses: Disapproval of praying against people by name","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Salih reported: A man mentioned Al-Hajjaj or others to his father, Ahmad ibn Hanbal, may Allah be pleased with him, saying, \u201cLet him be cursed!\u201d Ahmad said, \u201cI do not like for it to be uttered.\u201d Then, Ahmad said, \u201cSurely, the curse of Allah is upon the wrongdoers.\u201d (11:18) Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2723,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/31\/do-not-curse-lord-of-time\/","url_meta":{"origin":32169,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Cursing: Do not curse time, Allah is Time","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty said: The son of Adam insults Me. He curses time, but I am time, for in My hand are the night and day.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\